9287.name: T.I.B.B.E.R.S (B.E.E.G Edition)
9287.description:
Summons Enraged Robo-Tibbers. Robo-Tibbers swipes, dealing area damage. Enraged Robo-Tibbers focuses on enemies with the most health and grows larger, faster and deals more damage over the duration.
